(41, 1, 'Đi dạo trong ngành IT 5: Data Science', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Phần 1:</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp; Đi dạo v&ograve;ng quanh Data Scientist?</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Phần 2:</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> C&ocirc;ng việc chủ yếu của Data Scientist c&oacute; phải l&agrave; c&agrave;o data?</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Phần 3:</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> C&aacute;c kiến thức cần thiết để trở th&agrave;nh Data Scientist</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Phần 4:</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Tố chất của một Data Scientist</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-77822e16-7fff-f28b-5add-1dda429f1e48\"></span></p>', '<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Phần 1:&nbsp; Đi dạo v&ograve;ng quanh Data Scientist?</span></h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Data Scientist l&agrave; nghề sexy nhất của thế kỉ 21, theo Harvard Business Review nhận định. Với skillset chuy&ecirc;n s&acirc;u v&agrave; trải d&agrave;i tr&ecirc;n nhiều lĩnh vực, c&aacute;c Data Scientist (nh&agrave; khoa học dữ liệu) cũng được v&iacute; &ldquo;qu&yacute; hiếm như kỳ l&acirc;n&rdquo;. B&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y ch&uacute;ng ta sẽ c&ugrave;ng nhau l&agrave;m r&otilde;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 6.5196850393700885pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Data Scientist l&agrave; g&igrave;? C&ocirc;ng việc cụ thể của họ?</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 6.5196850393700885pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Những tố chất v&agrave; kỹ năng cần thiết?</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 6.5196850393700885pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Học g&igrave; để trở th&agrave;nh một Data Scientist?</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border: none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 602px; height: 345px;\"><img style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/fY_QNej0-JHQ5FO51DSHrIW2YCqlT8u8xS2sFPrhhqDtJwPdA0k87c9wuk5DpnDyxD_NYUfesq_obotsfgBna0VdHti2zsDrHSrEIxQ4Pqgld4mc9cvaYN0vU9p8utLi9mYu6_OG\" width=\"602\" height=\"345\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">DATA SCIENTIST L&Agrave; G&Igrave;?</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Data Scientist l&agrave; người tạo ra gi&aacute; trị từ data, với hai nhiệm vụ ch&iacute;nh l&agrave;:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -7.653543307086622pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Thu thập, xử l&yacute; dữ liệu để t&igrave;m ra những insight gi&aacute; trị.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">V&iacute; dụ, dựa tr&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng tin thu thập được từ c&aacute;c post/comment/status tr&ecirc;n mạng x&atilde; hội, Data Scientist c&oacute; thể t&igrave;m ra được: cứ gần đến ng&agrave;y Valentine th&igrave; tần suất xuất hiện của&nbsp; thương hiệu ABC cao hơn hẳn.Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; một insight gi&aacute; trị m&agrave; bộ phận Marketing c&oacute; thể sử dụng cho c&aacute;c chiến dịch quảng c&aacute;o trong m&ugrave;a Valentine.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -7.653543307086622pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Giải th&iacute;ch, tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y những insight đ&oacute; cho c&aacute;c b&ecirc;n li&ecirc;n quan, để chuyển h&oacute;a insight th&agrave;nh h&agrave;nh động.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">V&iacute; dụ, khi t&igrave;m ra được insight gi&aacute; trị từ data, bạn cần l&agrave;m report/presentation, hay visualization để biểu diễn, giải th&iacute;ch cho c&aacute;c b&ecirc;n li&ecirc;n quan hiểu được: 1) Insight đ&oacute; l&agrave; g&igrave;, c&oacute; &yacute; nghĩa g&igrave;? 2) C&oacute; thể ứng dụng cụ thể như thế n&agrave;o để đem lại lợi &iacute;ch cho doanh nghiệp/sản phẩm/người d&ugrave;ng.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, Data Scientist l&agrave; nghề rất mới, n&ecirc;n định nghĩa về n&oacute; c&ograve;n kh&aacute; mơ hồ (ngay cả tr&ecirc;n thế giới). V&igrave; vậy, t&ugrave;y theo từng c&ocirc;ng ty m&agrave; m&ocirc; tả c&ocirc;ng việc, y&ecirc;u cầu skillset, thậm ch&iacute; job title c&oacute; thể kh&aacute;c nhau đ&ocirc;i ch&uacute;t.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">SỰ KH&Aacute;C BIỆT GIỮA DATA ANALYST V&Agrave; DATA SCIENTIST</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Đ&uacute;ng l&agrave; hai c&ocirc;ng việc n&agrave;y c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhiệm tương đối giống nhau. Ở một số c&ocirc;ng ty, </span><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://itviec.com/it-jobs/data-scientist?utm_source=blogpost&amp;utm_medium=center_post&amp;utm_campaign=linktosite\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Data Scientist</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> c&oacute; khi cũng l&agrave; </span><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://itviec.com/it-jobs/data-analyst?utm_source=blogpost&amp;utm_medium=center_post&amp;utm_campaign=linktosite\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Data Analyst</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, hoặc thậm ch&iacute; c&oacute; thể nhập nhằng với cả Machine Learning Engineer, </span><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://itviec.com/it-jobs/data-engineer?utm_source=blogpost&amp;utm_medium=center_post&amp;utm_campaign=linktosite\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Data Engineer</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> nữa.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">C&aacute; nh&acirc;n m&igrave;nh th&igrave; nghĩ </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Data Scientist chia l&agrave;m 2 dạng ch&iacute;nh</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, tạm gọi nh&aacute;nh A (Analysis) v&agrave; nh&aacute;nh B (Building), cụ thể:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -14.740157480314956pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Data Scientist nh&aacute;nh A (Analysis)</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> l&agrave; những thinker. Nhiệm vụ ch&iacute;nh của họ l&agrave; ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch dữ liệu bằng c&aacute;c phương ph&aacute;p thống k&ecirc; để t&igrave;m ra insight gi&aacute; trị.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; margin-left: 3.2598425196850442pt; text-indent: -18pt; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border: 1pt solid #000000; filter: brightness(1.22) contrast(0.59); display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 539px; height: 42px;\"><img style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-4VcqZgdHsQ-DnWb2AWPHDcubujWcWK_DOALqapxPT1YWRFokwsL-O66jqecusobbg5UzCRNHDhVPrar5F-YW1ONXWOZEDRtxpk3xZ-vcnxUj2MXKliHRVFk-U4tJweQAF1npreD\" width=\"539\" height=\"42\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -14.740157480314956pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Data Scientist nh&aacute;nh B (Building)</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> thường mạnh về software engineering hơn. Họ đảm nhiệm việc xử l&yacute;/lưu trữ data, viết code/thuật to&aacute;n cho c&aacute;c sản phẩm data của c&ocirc;ng ty.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border: 1pt solid #000000; filter: opacity(0.93); display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 539px; height: 64px;\"><img style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/r0BCnb7j39QilfD4VKSLU_ty9BO4ZnxKAX9OmvBiiZ142ShBkBgmb51lih8QZfa6LKRfFeb9EzFGOETdAsv5opCpqk6f_WHSdnvcb2svCuRSzU08D4Shr5H6bVSNIvfxWCXBpz-r\" width=\"539\" height=\"64\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p 