-type: decimal; font-size: 13pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y kh&aacute;i niệm bảng c&acirc;n đối kế to&aacute;n l&agrave; g&igrave;?</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 13pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Định nghĩa t&agrave;i sản cố định? Đ&acirc;u l&agrave; ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; đ&aacute;nh gi&aacute; một t&agrave;i sản l&agrave; t&agrave;i sản cố định?</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 13pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.799